sub_title: Jeugd-en gezinsprofessional- met SKJ register(Tigrinya sprekend)
summary:
I have studied Social works and Sociology and have a long work experience in the field of child, family and community services. I followed Migration managent Course at the university of Maastricht, too. 
More over, I am a Certified trainer of Psycho-education, 7Roses Empowerment Strategies (trauma), Parenting between two cultures, family mediation, domestic violence, empowerment trainings, intercultural mediation, advices for ( Eritrean) migrants and for professionals/organisations working with refugees.
I am also a certified VCA-Nederlands (Occupational Safety & Health in the work place) trainer in Tigrinya for the Eritrean Target group.
